# Normalize line endings: store text as LF in the repo and check it out as LF
# on every platform (including Windows), so diffs stay clean and gofmt/gofumpt
# are consistent everywhere. git auto-detects text vs binary by content.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Belt-and-suspenders for common binary assets git might otherwise sniff wrong.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.gz   binary
*.zip  binary
